      <body>
         <div type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="Edgeworth_NLS_23131_XXXX-08-14_page01.jpg"/>
            <opener>
               <dateline>
                  <placeName ref="./Placeography.xml#Rokeby-Park_ENK">Rokeby Park</placeName><lb/>
                  <date>14<hi rend= "superscript">th</hi> August</date></dateline><lb/>
               <salute>
Dear Sir<lb/>
               </salute>
            </opener>
            <p>On my return from <placeName ref="./Placeography.xml#Ramsgate_ENK">Ramsgate</placeName> I only<lb/>
               remained a few hours in <unclear></unclear> Place tho little<lb/>
               time to make up <persName ref="./Personography.xml#EdgeM1">Miss <choice><orig>Edgeworths</orig><reg>Edgeworth's</reg></choice></persName> packet <hi rend="superscript">My</hi> <choice><orig>affect-<lb/>
                  ion</orig><reg>affection</reg></choice> to her and my illness and distress<lb/>
               <unclear>love</unclear> to her and my illness and distress<lb/>
               must be my excuse for not performing my<lb/>
               promise of sending the letters by you but<lb/>
               they are perfectly safe and if on my<lb/>
               return to town I find she is not returning<lb/>
               with <persName ref="./Personography.xml#EdgeF3" cert="medium">M<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi>. Wilson</persName> I shall send them per<lb/>
               favour of <persName ref="./Personography.xml#FreeF1">Sir Francis Freeling</persName><lb/>            
            </p>
            <closer>
               Sincerely Yours<lb/>
               <persName ref="./Personography.xml#LockS1"><choice><orig>C.</orig><reg>Charlotte</reg></choice> Sophia Lockhart</persName><lb/>
            </closer>
         </div>
      </body>
